edu.rit.numeric.plot

  • Packages that use edu.rit.numeric.plot 
    Package Description
    edu.rit.numeric.plot
    Package edu.rit.numeric.plot provides classes and interfaces for plotting data.
    edu.rit.numeric.plot.impl
    Package edu.rit.numeric.plot.impl provides low-level implementation classes for the high-level plotting classes in package edu.rit.numeric.plot.
  • Classes in edu.rit.numeric.plot used by edu.rit.numeric.plot 
    Class and Description
    Dots
    Class Dots provides operations for creating several common shapes of dots for plotting points.
    Plot
    Class Plot is a class for creating and displaying a plot.
    Plot.AxisKind
    Enum Plot.AxisKind enumerates the possible kinds of axis on a Plot.
